call_input_c(part_count, filename)

Returns the C call required to use this IO module for input. This solely calls the random_io function defined in the required header file for this module.

Returns

The function call used for this module.

Return type

str

call_output_c(part_count, filename)

Returns the C call required to use this IO module for output. In this case output is not supported so an empty string is returned.

Returns

Empty string

Return type

str

gen_code_c(part_type)

Returns the C code required for this IO module. This IO module uses a prewritten C implementation so has no C output.
